quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  33,59,"O Prophet! Tell your wives and your daughters and the women of believers to put on their outer-garments over their bodies in such a way that they are recognised and not molested.h And Allah is Forgiving, Merciful"
  33,60,"If the hypocrites and those in whose hearts is a disease and those who spread rumours and trouble in Madinah desist not, We shall certainly urge you on against them. And then they shall not be your neighbours therein but for a little while"
  33,61,"Accursed, they will be seized and slain wherever found"
  33,62,That was the way Allah dealt with those who have gone before. And you will find no change in Allah's way
  33,63,"People ask you about the Hour (the time when the present world will end and the Hereafter begin). Say, \"Information about it is only with Allah. And what do you know, the Hour may be nigh"
  33,64,Allah has indeed cursed the suppressors of Truth and prepared for them a burning Fire
  33,65,They will abide therein forever. They will find neither a wali nor anyone to help
  33,66,"That day when their faces are turned about in the Fire, they will say, \"Woe to us! Would that we had obeyed Allah and obeyed the Messenger"
  33,67,"And they will say, \"Our Lord! We only obeyed our bosses and our seniors. And they led us astray from the right path"
  33,68,Our Lord! Give them a double punishment and give them a severe curse